# Proving artifacts for in-browser snarkjs (FIN-027, option 2).
# The .wasm (witness generators) are small and committed; the .zkey (proving keys)
# are large (shield 31MB / unshield 64MB / transfer 110MB) and DEMO-only
# (single-party ceremony, invariant #10) — never committed. The operator copies
# them here from the Railway `ceremony` container (or a local setup:ceremony):
#   setup/build/<circuit>/<circuit>.zkey  ->  public/artifacts/<circuit>/<circuit>.zkey
*.zkey
